---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import site from '../../config/site.json';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Solarelites Privacy Policy – how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." noIndex={true}>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display font-800 text-5xl tracking-tight mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-12" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>Solarelites collects information you provide directly when you fill out our contact forms, request quotes, or engage our services. This includes your name, phone number, email address, property address, and energy consumption details.</p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide solar installation quotes and consultations</li>
          <li>Process government subsidy applications on your behalf</li>
          <li>Communicate about your project status</li>
          <li>Send relevant information about solar schemes and updates (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our services and website</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Government bodies (MNRE, DISCOM) for subsidy applications — with your explicit consent</li>
          <li>Certified installation partners who assist with your project</li>
          <li>Service providers who assist us in operating our website</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorised access, alteration, or disclosure. All data is stored securely and access is restricted to authorised personnel only.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and analyse website traffic. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`}>{site.contact.email}</a> or call <a href={`tel:${site.contact.phoneRaw}`}>{site.contact.phone}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
